

Car Selling App
Author: Felix Mutuku

Description
The Car Selling App is a web application that facilitates the buying and selling of cars online. It provides a platform for both car dealers and individual sellers to list their vehicles and for potential buyers to browse, search, and purchase cars. The app offers various features, including user registration, car listings, detailed car information, image uploads, and communication between buyers and sellers.

Project Setup Instructions
To run the Car Selling App locally on your machine, follow these steps:

Clone the repository to your local machine using git clone https://github.com/Felix-Mutuku/car-selling-app.git.

Navigate to the project directory with cd car-selling-app.

Install the required dependencies using npm install.

Set up the environment variables and database connection details (if applicable).

Start the development server with npm start.

Access the app in your web browser at http://localhost:3000.

Live Site
The live version of the Car Selling App can be found on GitHub Pages at https://Felix-Mutuku.github.io/car-selling-app.

